end/sleep/hibernate. If cat /sys/power/mem_sleep return [s2idle] deep This confirms that the default suspend mode...","thumb_url":"https://weiguangcui.github.io/img/Me.jpg","blocks":null,"service_name":"weiguangcui.github.io","thumb_width":490,"thumb_height":653,"from_url":"https://weiguangcui.github.io/2019-03-10-ubuntu-laptop-power-management/","original_url":"https://weiguangcui.github.io/2019-03-10-ubuntu-laptop-power-management/"}],"team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"cRP"}]},{"client_msg_id":"6820b6ec-b4fa-4b53-a260-c72ec9616447","type":"message","user":"U03C6TEAZ","text":"systemd になってから簡単になった感じする。","ts":"1603730949.056500","team":"T03C4RC8V","reactions":[{"name":"desune","count":1,"users":["U8CC7MDCL"]}],"replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"XG2nz"}]},{"client_msg_id":"a1dc9abc-76b3-4703-af19-9e3663003188","type":"message","user":"U016GRZN0GJ","text":"ちょっと前からswapデバイスのUUIDがいるようになったのでコピー\n```$ grep swap /etc/fstab | tail -n 1\nUUID=ea0ecfc3-0059-4272-8d3a-847b128e0100 none            swap    sw              0       0```\n /etc/default/grub を編集して resume=UUID=.... にUUIDコピペ\n```GRUB_CMDLINE_LINUX_DEFAULT=\"quiet splash resume=UUID=ea0ecfc3-0059-4272-8d3a-847b128e0100\"```\ngrub 更新\n```$ sudo update-grub```\n ハイバネートのテスト\n```$ systemctl hibernate```\nラップトップの蓋閉じたらハイバネート\n/etc/systemd/logind.conf を編集\n```HandleLidSwitch=hibernate```\n","ts":"1603728508.055800","edited":{"user":"U016GRZN0GJ","ts":"1603729151.000000"},"team":"T03C4RC8V","reactions":[{"name":"tiken","count":3,"users":["U9S4G0LJW","UEB0VGD7E","U01BASA3F9T"]}],"replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"EBXZ"}]},{"client_msg_id":"ec996bbd-ed41-4fdf-8e19-7d03982f2e6c","type":"message","user":"U016GRZN0GJ","text":"hibernateのやりかた毎回やってるので覚えてしまった","ts":"1603727945.048600","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"b